Insert a temporary working directory template

Source: R/rstudio-addins.R
insert_examplesTempdir_template.Rd

This function inserts a template for the @examplesTempdir tag at the cursor position. It's designed to be used as an RStudio addin.

Usage

insert_examplesTempdir_template()
